  "text": "The Plant Cell [CITATION_1] , identified the existence of a plastid transit peptide with a proposed cleavage site between Val-59 and Cys-60 in CRTR-B1 and Val-57 and Cys-58 in CRTR-B2. The sequences of the predicted mature polypeptides after cleavage of the transit sequences are 94% similar and 86% identical.",
